						               													<description>User Summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This freely downloadable  expansion for the print-and-play game Glider-Pit Gladiators (GPG) allows players to create and play continuing gladiator characters who can gain experience and special skills over the course of their careers. The game was first web published in 1999 and updated in 2002.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Campaign Expansion adds rules covering survival, experience, and special abilities and advantages. A system is included for generating random experienced gladiator characters so that players can start with characters having some special abilities and advantages. Finally, there are two new optional rules: throwing attack fumbles and gladiator retirement.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The complete expansion can be downloaded from the BGG files section, below.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
